Package cmput301.textbookhub.Models

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NamedItem
    Created by Fred on 2016/2/29.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bid
    Bid is used to return the bid amount, bidder, bid time made from User on a Textbook.
    BidList
    BidList used to keep a list of bids which are associated with a Textbook.
    BookShelf
    BookShelf used to keep a list of Textbooks and aide in the manipulation of textbooks.
    DataHelper
    DataHelper is used to upload and download information to/from Elastic Search.
    DataHelper.AddTextbookTask
    Add a Textbook(s) to the ElasticSearch server.
    DataHelper.AddUserTask
    Adds User(s) to the ElasticSearch server
    DataHelper.DeleteTextbookTask
    Delete Textbook(s) from the ElasticSearch server.
    DataHelper.GetAllTextbookTask
    Get all Textbook(s) from the ElasticSearch server.
    DataHelper.GetBiddedTextbookByBidderTask
    Get bidded Textbook(s) by a specific bidder from the ElasticSearch server.
    DataHelper.GetTextbookByBorrowerTask
    Get Textbook(s) currently borrowed from by a specific User from the ElasticSearch server.
    DataHelper.GetTextbookTask
    Get Textbook(s) from the ElasticSearch server.
    DataHelper.GetUserTask
    Get User(s) from the ElasticSearch server.
    DataHelper.SearchTextbookTask
    Search for Textbook(s) from the ElasticSearch server.
    DataHelper.TestServerConnectionTask
    This class is used mainly to test server connectivity
    DataHelper.UpdateTextbookTask
    Update the Textbook(s) information on ElasticSearch from local memory.
    DataHelper.UpdateUserTask
    Update the information of the current User on the ElasticSearch server.
    OfflineCommandList
    OfflineCommandList is used to handle offline behaviour.
    OfflineHelper
    OfflineHelper is used to save offline changes to local memory
    OfflineNewTextbookCommand
    OfflineNewTextbookCommand is used to send commands from OfflineHelper to DataHelper
    Textbook
    Textbook is the item user own or borrowed.
    Textbook.Builder
    The builder is used to build a Textbook
    User
    User is the user of the application, and contains lists of Textbook.
